video.title: Padmasambhava - Guru Rinpoche - Ascending with the Conduct
video.description:
Another clear and powerful terma treasure teaching from the text "Dakini Teachings" (translated by Erik Pema Kunsang).

Teaching entitled - "First of All - Ascending with the Conduct."
Teaching/reading put to music and intended for deep meditation

Music by: Meditative Mind - www.bandcamp.com
